title: Bloodhound’s Regression Instinct
description: Bloodhound’s Regression Instinct Manhwa “Yan,” the protagonist, was brainwashed by the emperor and lived as his puppet. After finding out he was being played by the emperor, he planned to seek revenge, but collapsed due to the emperor’s might. He thought he had died, but when he woke up, he realized he had regressed to the time when he was a recruit. Whether to seek revenge on the emperor or to find his family. The choice lay in his hands. The Returning Instinct of a Hound , The Return Instinct of the Hunting Dog, 사냥개의 회귀본능
